<title>
Warning / Indicator Light Description
</title>
<ptxt>
There are three warning and one indicator lights controlled by ESP<sup>®</sup> hydraulic unit / control module assembly in combination meter. They give warning and indication to driver by changing their modes: light ON / blinking / light OFF.
</ptxt>
